<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('./includes/head'); %>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #e63946;
      --navy: #1d3557;
      --light-blue: #a8dadc;
      --border: #e0e0e0;
      --bg: #f8f9fa;
      --text-main: #2b2d42;
      --text-muted: #6c757d;
      --transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    }

    /* Added Smooth Scrolling for the About Us link */
    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      color: var(--text-main);
      background-color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }

    /* --- Navigation --- */
    header {
      height: 70px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    .header-content {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--primary);
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--navy);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: var(--transition);
    }

    nav a:hover { color: var(--primary); }

    .login-btn {
      border: 1.5px solid var(--primary);
      padding: 8px 20px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      color: var(--primary) !important;
    }

    .login-btn:hover {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #fff !important;
    }

    /* --- Hero Section --- */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      padding: 100px 0;
      background: linear-gradient(rgba(29, 53, 87, 0.7), rgba(29, 53, 87, 0.7)), 
                  url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542314831-068cd1dbfeeb?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .hero-flex {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 60px;
    }

    .hero-text { flex: 1; }

    .hero-text h2 {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .hero-text p {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .hero-img-wrapper {
      flex: 1;
      display: block;
    }

    .hero-img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 400px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .btn {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: var(--transition);
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.4);
    }

    /* --- Features --- */
    .features { padding: 80px 0; background: var(--bg); }

    .features-title {
      font-size: 28px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--navy);
    }

    .feature-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .feature-card {
      padding: 32px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: var(--transition);
    }

    .feature-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      border-color: var(--primary);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    .feature-card h4 {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: var(--navy);
    }

    .feature-card p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    /* --- Footer --- */
    footer {
      background: var(--navy);
      color: #e0e0e0;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }

    .footer-flex {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    /* --- Responsive --- */
    @media (max-width: 992px) {
      .hero-flex { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
      .hero-text h2 { font-size: 36px; }
      .hero-img-wrapper { display: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="container header-content">
      <a href="#" class="logo">Hot-Stay</a>
      <nav>
        <a href="#about">About Us</a>
        <a href="/Hot-Stay/login" class="login-btn">Login</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-flex">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <h2>Book Better, <br>Travel Simpler.</h2>
        <p>Verified stays with transparent pricing. Join 50k+ travelers exploring the world with Hot-Stay.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-img-wrapper">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1566073771259-6a8506099945?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" class="hero-img" alt="Luxury Hotel">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <h3 class="features-title">Why Travelers Trust Us</h3>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h4>Vetted Listings</h4>
          <p>Every home is hand-verified for quality, safety, and high-speed Wi-Fi standards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h4>Best Rates</h4>
          <p>Direct partnerships with hosts mean you save up to 15% compared to other platforms.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h4>24/7 Support</h4>
          <p>Not a bot. A real human team is ready to help you via chat, anytime, anywhere.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h4>Easy Returns</h4>
          <p>Plans change. Enjoy flexible cancellation options on over 80% of our properties.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="container footer-flex">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Hot-Stay International. Proudly made for travelers.</p>
      <div>
        <a href="#" style="color: inherit; margin-left: 20px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px;">Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="#" style="color: inherit; margin-left: 20px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px;">Terms of Service</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>